sub_title: Master of many trades, lover of Make-up Artistry & Educating. Currently cooking up a Trinbagonian storm in Amsterdam.
summary:
I am very well experienced in my fields of Make-up, Management, Leadership, Teaching & Customer Service. I enjoy both the application and the teaching of Make-up Artistry. I have had a burning passion since the tender age of 16 for this art.

I've completed Business Management studies and have recently launched a basic cosmetic range for Darker Skin tones. These experiences have increased my drive for Project Management, Research and New Product Development. 

Management and Leadership is a strong point of my character and professional development. I have been fortunate to gain knowledge and experience in various industries as a Team Leader and/or Manager whilst working for companies or managing projects.

My short term goals are to gain employment with an organisation that will support, develop and enhance my management and leadership skills. Continue with the manufacture and distribution of PerfectFaces' products and services en ontwikkel mijn begrip en beheersing van de Nederlandse taal.
